title: Arkansas' Greenlaw is SEC Freshman of the Week
text:
Southeastern Conference names Arkansas linebacker Greenlaw the Freshman of the Week THE ASSOCIATED PRESS First Posted: October 26, 2015 - 3:08 pmLast Updated: October 26, 2015 - 3:08 pm We also have more stories about: (click the phrases to see a list) 
Organizations: 
Arkansas (508) 

FAYETTEVILLE, Arkansas â€” University of Arkansas freshman linebacker Dre Greenlaw has been named the Southeastern Conference Freshman of the Week. 
Greenlaw was announced Monday as the winner of the award after making 16 tackles during the Razorbacks' four-overtime win over Auburn. 
Greenlaw made 12 of the tackles during the second half and the overtime as Arkansas beat Auburn 54-46.
